11#ifndef MODULES_AUDIO_CODING_AUDIO_NETWORK_ADAPTOR_INCLUDE_AUDIO_NETWORK_ADAPTOR_H_
12#define MODULES_AUDIO_CODING_AUDIO_NETWORK_ADAPTOR_INCLUDE_AUDIO_NETWORK_ADAPTOR_H_
13
14#include "absl/types/optional.h"
15#include "api/audio_codecs/audio_encoder.h"
16#include "modules/audio_coding/audio_network_adaptor/include/audio_network_adaptor_config.h"
17
18namespace webrtc {
19
20// An AudioNetworkAdaptor optimizes the audio experience by suggesting a
21// suitable runtime configuration (bit rate, frame length, FEC, etc.) to the
22// encoder based on network metrics.
23class AudioNetworkAdaptor {
24 public:
25 virtual ~AudioNetworkAdaptor() = default;
26
27 virtual void SetUplinkBandwidth(int uplink_bandwidth_bps) = 0;
28
29 virtual void SetUplinkPacketLossFraction(
30 float uplink_packet_loss_fraction) = 0;
31
32 virtual void SetRtt(int rtt_ms) = 0;
33
34 virtual void SetTargetAudioBitrate(int target_audio_bitrate_bps) = 0;
35
36 virtual void SetOverhead(size_t overhead_bytes_per_packet) = 0;
37
38 virtual AudioEncoderRuntimeConfig GetEncoderRuntimeConfig() = 0;
39
40 virtual void StartDebugDump(FILE* file_handle) = 0;
41
42 virtual void StopDebugDump() = 0;
43
44 virtual ANAStats GetStats() const = 0;
45};
46
47} // namespace webrtc
48
49#endif // MODULES_AUDIO_CODING_AUDIO_NETWORK_ADAPTOR_INCLUDE_AUDIO_NETWORK_ADAPTOR_H_
